<paragraph id="IAS01_BC13T" principles="no"><paranum>BC13T</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="BC13T"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS01_BC13T_P0001" outputclass="keep_with_next">Because the amendments do not substantively change existing requirements,       the Board decided that:</p><ol type="lower-alpha"><li id="IAS01_BC13T_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value><p>prospective application is appropriate;</p>         </li><li id="IAS01_BC13T_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value><p>a long implementation period is unnecessary; and</p></li><li id="IAS01_BC13T_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value><p>early adoption of the amendments should be permitted.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>